# .mailmap consolidates commit identities for display in
#   git log / git blame / `git shortlog -s`
# and in GitHub's contributors graph.
#
# We collapse the Dependabot bot into the primary maintainer so the
# contributors graph reflects human contribution, not automated
# dependency bumps. Dinesh, a real external contributor, is kept as
# a distinct identity.
#
# Format:
#   <Canonical Name> <canonical-email>  <old-email>

